 regex always matched first. Added targeted test.","+- **MEDIUM fixed:** Missing CLI args edge case for empty model/cwd.","+- **MEDIUM (not fixed):** `classifyError` exported as public in codex.ts but module-private in claude-code.ts — inconsistent API surface.","+- **LOW (not fixed):** Duplicated `classifyError` logic and `NETWORK_CODES` set between codex.ts and claude-code.ts.","+- **Coverage:** codex.ts at 100% statements/lines/functions, 96.03% branches. Overall 96.74%.","+- **Architecture concern:** Tests mock `child_process.spawn` directly despite story anti-pattern note.","+","+## Token Report — code-review","+- Total tool calls: 21","+- By tool: Bash: 8, Read: 13, Edit: 3, Glob: 1","+- Largest Bash outputs: `npx vitest run --coverage` (~30 lines), `npx vitest run` (~15 lines), `codeharness coverage` (~4 lines)","+- Files read: 13 unique, 15 total reads (codex-driver.test.ts read 3x)","+- Redundant operations: one extra coverage check could have been combined","+"," ### 12-1-codex-driver-implementation — dev-story (2026-04-03T13:00)"," "," - **Boundary test catch-block enforcement**: All catch blocks need `// IGNORE:` comments. Fixed in 4 catch blocks in codex.ts."]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
